      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. we did check the staff and the counting procedures and everything seems fine on that end. people are saying it's weird because it's so consistent but never enough to trigger a major red flag in the system. it's like the items just... vanish in small amounts. any other ideas for what could cause this kind of \"phantom\" shrinkage?",
